{"tid":2174595,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"積金鏈難完全脫美  面臨查倉中止投資 港官MPF陷困局","createTime":"2020-08-26T03:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T04:23:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1c4823b8f34f46b72a3eabde6974d8e23a19ca","tid":2174595,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/ICJ44ZBXZNECRGCNSSQCPXHTAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FICJ44ZBXZNECRGCNSSQCPXHTAI%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDhq8xf71D2STVxQEH8iwqLk%3D&h=77132c75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FICJ44ZBXZNECRGCNSSQCPXHTAI%2F&h=80290243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/ICJ44ZBXZNECRGCNSSQCPXHTAI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n積金鏈難完全脫美 <br />\n面臨查倉中止投資 港官MPF陷困局<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】拒絕與11名被制裁中港官員「斬纜」，而可能落入美國第二輪制裁清單的金融機構，不僅限於銀行，範圍可覆蓋證券、外滙、期貨及中介經紀活動等投資機構，何謂保持重大交易亦由美方定義。與打工仔一樣，高官按例亦須參與強積金（MPF）或公積金（ORSO）計劃，制裁令下，其戶口可能因受託人、基金公司或產品發行商，涉足美元資產或投資經理是美資機構而受到牽連。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：金融業界：制裁主菜10月揭盅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W3tf1CMzimnGVinzVICcVQ5zd2c=/881x1196/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7AJMOSC4GBAX3MQ4KFUGPF4IQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW3tf1CMzimnGVinzVICcVQ5zd2c%3D%2F881x1196%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7AJMOSC4GBAX3MQ4KFUGPF4IQY.jpg&h=71febaa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■11名受制裁高官包括林鄭月娥、鄭若驊、李家超和鄧炳強等的積金戶口，若有涉足美元資產或投資經理是美資機構都會受牽連。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n有不願具名的強積金業界憂慮，強積金條例下，受託人不能如銀行般，自行暫停受制裁高官戶口，而投資過程亦難完全迴避美資公。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n現行條例不容許強積金計劃成員，於65歲退休前提取強積金，即受。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bRFDjMheWTT4ln8_WXXuFgvitmc=/1267x934/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PO3ZMB5OJFEGXFTSIS2VHJXTA4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbRFDjMheWTT4ln8_WXXuFgvitmc%3D%2F1267x934%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPO3ZMB5OJFEGXFTSIS2VHJXTA4.png&h=42772f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n積金局：注視措施影響<br />\n<br />\n積金局發言人回應查詢時表示，美國單方面制裁措施對本港並無法律效力，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府2016年起委託BCT銀聯、中銀保誠及永明金融為公務員的強積金及。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n三間受託人中，BCT銀聯屬全華資機構，中銀保誠為中銀香港及保誠「中英合資」的機構，永。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n業內人士估計，外資受託人或因母公司壓力需就制裁措施採取行動，以最極端情況估計，「上至受託人、基金公司，下至基金買。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n為安全計，受制裁人士可考慮大部份資產均投資以現金為主的港元貨幣。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nBCT銀聯回覆本報稱，正研究美國相關制裁內容，不便評論。永明金融發言人亦對事件不予置評，中銀保誠未有回覆查詢。"},{"pid":"c61be477f8f194efb316dde5b3a2bbad676b10f1","tid":2174595,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"個戇鳩法例只係唔俾市民提早取回強積金，我就唔信連官方單方面 cut 戶口都唔俾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f4be3a12fc489deeb782140f433455cd31125d","tid":2174595,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"只可投資大中華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港股連盈富都買唔到"},{"pid":"5041a0314a3072c6e828300c45c96c7600ccfe6c","tid":2174595,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c61be477f8f194efb316dde5b3a2bbad676b10f1","tid":2174595,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:11:29.000Z","msg":"個戇鳩法例只係唔俾市民提早取回強積金，我就唔信連官方單方面 cut 戶口都唔俾囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"改法例"},{"pid":"489de7aa68af85ae5ef880b829c3afa527d64073","tid":2174595,"uid":101945,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:17:57.000Z","msg":"新增勝利11人基金 - ALL RMB 中國國債"},{"pid":"43f68d83719256dff343fef2